import re
def solve(date):
    pattern = r'(\d{4})-(\d{2})-(\d{2})'
    match = re.search(pattern, date)
    if match:
        year = match.group(1)
        month = match.group(2)
        day = match.group(3)
        return day + '-' + month + '-' + year
    else:
        return "Invalid date format."
